name: RED LEGS
description:
Red Legs is a Photomanipulation Project for fasion photography. Using the photographs that i shot and making a digital collage with them. Red colour is used for the stronger contrast fasion image. Model is digitally coppied so there can be a dance in the dark sky. Women are just an object for the fashion designers and I wantted to criticise this fact on in this process. Nowadays this is called fashion.
